title: Swirl Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description: The Swirl Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art piece exudes a more “abstract” style with its unique layout. Artfully crafted from tough steel and molded into shape with intricate precision. This large focal piece is perfectly suited to living rooms, dining rooms, or wherever else you need a large masterpiece for decorative purposes. With its characterizing details inspired by iconic Atlantis. The Swirl Metal Art piece is guaranteed to catch the gaze of anyone nearby. The piece uses a circular shape made up of three separate swirls, and interconnecting are precisely cut lines that finish with three shapes – the primary colored components of the design. These colors are chosen by you from a selection of mesmerizing “candy” shades. Choose a color that matches your decor and preferences. Crafting something as abstract as this Swirl piece requires patience and dedication. Your very own Swirl metal art is the result of hard work and exceptional talent which you can flaunt in your home.

title: Eagle Head Oval by Dugout Creek Designs
description: An Eagle represents freedom, courage, honesty, and truthfulness. This Eagle Head Oval by Dugout Creek Designs Metal Art Decor depicts an eagle's head with its beak open. The detailing is beautiful, showcasing the feathers, eye, and beak with precise cut-outs. Finishing this design is an oval border for a complete look. The Eagle Head Oval Metal Art Decor was crafted by hand in the USA using quality steel material. It showcases the raw beauty and ferocity of an eagle in all its glory. Anyone who loves eagles would be absolutely delighted to have one of these hanging up in their home. It looks great as both a standalone or accenting wall decoration. The Eagle Head Oval comes in hammered black or rust patina based on your preferences.

title: Road Runner Oval by Dugout Creek Designs
description: The Road Runner Oval by Dugout Creek Designs Metal Art is a piece inspired by the famous "Road Runner" from the Looney Tunes cartoon series. The roadrunner is, in fact, a real bird - a species of fast-running ground cuckoos. They are typically found in the desert, just like in the cartoon adaptation! This metal art piece depicts a road runner mid-run within an oval frame. It's a very detailed artwork - you can even see the outline of the beak, talons, wing, and tail in the design. Such detail can only be accomplished by experienced metal artisans, found right here in the USA. The Road Runner Metal Art Decor is a smaller decoration suitable either as a standalone or as an accent to larger pieces. It's available in either hammered black (perfect for modern decor) or rust patina (a lovely addition to antique or rustic-colored decor).

title: Desert Dancer Tina Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description: The Desert Dancer Tina Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art is truly a special design and one that is bound to liven up the look of your home. It features a desert dancer, who we've named "Tina," and she is definitely an exotic one.  Tina has unruly hair, a slender body curved in a dance position, and a instrument in her hand. This metal artwork has a primary copper brown color with accenting tones of your choice, including blue, copper, green, red, silver, and teal. These contrast beautifully against the brown for a shimmering display. The Desert Dancer "Tina" Metal Art is made from steel and would look fabulous on a wall as a focal artwork. Just wait for your guests to start talking about it the moment they see it! Tina is one of a set of three Desert Dancers by Meyerdirk Art.  Check out Cindi and Willie, they will make a great group of figures to decorate your space!

title: Sun Circle Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description: The Sun Circle Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art from our vast collection has a beautiful and trendy design depicting a sun, moon, and stars within a circle shape. The combination of these pleasant and aesthetic elements with the happy face of the moon creates a wonderful decoration for any home. Crafted in the USA using quality steel, the Sun Circle Metal Art is made entirely by hand. All in one, this metal art symbolizes immortality, eternity, and nature (the moon) as well as the mind and intellect (the sun). The Sun Circle Metal Art comes in the vibrant colors of candy blue, candy orange, candy yellow, and hammered black to match the theme of your home.

title: Petroglyph Ted Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description: Inspired by the various petroglyphs and cave paintings from around the United States, this Petroglyph Ted Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art is a striking artistic wonder that takes its viewer back in time to an era when these petroglyphs were a popular way of communicating and sharing stories. The Petroglyph "Ted" Metal Art Decor features a man holding tools/instruments and comes in various colorways. You can decide what story Ted is telling! Regardless, it makes a wonderfully unique wall decoration to any home. We have several petroglyph metal artworks available - you can combine these together to create your own unique "cave" story in the house, or enhance the presence of one by presenting it individually.

title: Sun Dogs (Large) Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description: Large and extravagant, this Sun Dogs (Large) Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art makes a definite statement to any home. The design features a sundogs-inspired style, with two circles in alignment with each other, yet separated by large swirls. These swirls come in different candy colors, like yellow, green, and purple. The Large Sundogs Metal Art Decor is heavily inspired by the sundogs phenomenon.  When two “sundogs” flank the sun with a halo-like impression. This atmospheric optical “illusion” is enough to take someone’s breath away from its beauty, and with this metal artwork, the same process is replicated using high-quality steel. Made by hand in the USA, the Large Sundogs Metal Art Decor is no doubt a unique decoration for the walls of your home, and with its large size, it definitely won’t go unnoticed by visitors, especially when placed in a common room/hallway.

These swirls come in different candy colors, like yellow, green, and purple. The Large Sundogs Metal Art Decor is heavily inspired by the sundogs phenomenon.  When two “sundogs” flank the sun with a halo-like impression. This atmospheric optical “illusion” is enough to take someone’s breath away from its beauty, and with this metal artwork, the same process is replicated using high-quality steel. Made by hand in the USA, the Large Sundogs Metal Art Decor is no doubt a unique decoration for the walls of your home, and with its large size, it definitely won’t go unnoticed by visitors, especially when placed in a common room/hallway.

title: William Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description:
The William Abstract Metal Art has a creative and versatile design, featuring 5 interchangeable metallic blocks that come in a wide range of candy colors and faux metallic finishes. With one purchase, you receive the entire artwork, including the 5 blocks – 3 in your chosen color and 2 in a neutral polished silver for contrast.

With its stunning abstract layout, the William Abstract Metal Art is a vastly unique design in comparison to many of our other pieces. It’s best suited to modern spaces, and with its large size, should be styled accordingly – such as over a fireplace, above a dining table, or in the entrance hallway as a primary focal point for guests and family members alike.

The William Abstract Metal Art, like all of our designs, is constructed using quality steel and put together by hand in the USA, where our talented team of metal artisans uses their skills to produce stunningly unique artworks.

Dimensions: 18" x 36"

title: Dark Side of the Moon Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description:
Looking up at the sky at night, have you ever wanted to just pluck that brilliant glowing orb and admire it up close? Well, we did our best to recreate the moon’s allure with this impressive Dark Side of the Moon Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art!

Set upon a solid black frame is a rough-cut distressed copper and silver circle with holes to mimic the moon’s craters. On top of that are delicate string-like curves supporting the candy-colored squares reminiscent of shooting stars.

title: Black Mesh Framed by The Nature Gallery
description:
Title:  "Black Mesh", this size being a 18" x 24" image, mounted, laminated (so no glass needed, no light reflection from surface).  Presented in a wood frame with linen liner.  Frame and liner add 2.5" in each dimension, so outside dimensions of the frame image is 23" x 29".  Image is signed and numbered from the edition of 250.
This is a closeup or macrophotograph of a mesh ball used in taking showers.  Actual area represented in the image is about 1/2 the size of a credit card.  Image is composed of 16 exposures to provide depth-of-field.  Pretty cool, eh!
The image is also offered here in my shop as an 22" x 30" framed piece, 18" x 24" gallery-wrap canvas, and a 22" x 30" gallery-wrap canvas.  I can custom-size anywhere in between or go larger.  Contact me and we can discussion options and do a virtual fitting into your space.

title: Standing Deer Buzz Blade by Dugout Creek Designs
description: The Standing Deer Buzz Blade by Dugout Creek Designs is heavily inspired by lodge-themed accents, detailing a lone deer standing amidst a forest with trees and mountains. The design is bordered by a creative buzz blade frame, which adds to the rustic "lodge" feeling of the metal art. Suitable for anyone who loves the woods or lodge-style metal art.  The Standing Deer Buzz Blade Metal Art decor is a stunning cabin-inspired piece that looks great when hung against a wooden background. This metal art decor is handmade from durable steel, and is a lovely addition to homes seeking rustic elements or even as a gift to a friend. Choose from the colors of distressed copper and rust patina for a rustic vibe or try the hammered black variant for a more modern expression.

description: This means the canvas wraps around the 1.5" deep stretcher frame, stapled on the back.  So when you hang it as is, all you see from whatever side, top or bottom you look, is image.  The stretcher bar is "keyed" meaning if the canvas were ever to loosen in taughtness (unlikely but remotely possible), it can be easily tightened without have to re-stretch the canvas.  The image is signed and numbered on the back from the limited edition of 250.

title: Ramen Blue Framed by The Nature Gallery
description: This presentation is an 18" x 24" Framed presentation.  The photograph is mounted to 3/16” foamcore and a matte lamination overlaid to reduce all reflections from the surface; no glass is used in hanging.  The image is set in a wood frame with a linen liner.  The image has the hanging system attached and provided with two hooks for hanging.  It is ready to be immediately hung in your space on arrival!  The image is signed and numbered from the limited edition of 250.

title: Ramen Blue Framed by The Nature Gallery
description: This presentation is a 24" x 30" Framed presentation.  The 24" x 30" photograph is mounted to 3/16” foamcore and a matte lamination overlaid to reduce all reflections from the surface; no glass is used in hanging.  The image is set in a wood frame with a linen liner that adds 2.5” to all sides, so the outside dimension of this framed presentation is 29” x 35”.  The image has the hanging system attached and provided with two hooks for hanging.  It is ready to be immediately hung in your space on arrival!  The image is signed and numbered from the limited edition of 250.

Buffalo Welcome Circle by Dugout Creek Designs
description: There's nothing like a Bison to welcome guests into your home or lodge. This Buffalo Welcome Circle by Dugout Creek Designs Metal Decor displays the outline/shadow of a bison inside a circle shape with the word "welcome" below. Each detail is hand-cut in the USA with quality steel, including the intricate tail, blades of grass, and typography. The Buffalo Welcome Circle Metal Art Decor could be placed at the entrance of your home, a cabin, or even a hunting lodge. The black hammered black option is ideal for modern or rustic homes, while the rust-brown tone is a perfect match for Adirondack style spaces. No wall art compares to the unique handiwork by our talented metal artisans. You can also take a look at our other metal art designs to find accenting pieces for this welcome sign.

title: Duck Welcome Circle by Dugout Creek Designs
description: Nothing beats welcoming your guests like this lovely Duck Welcome Circle by Dugout Creek Designs Metal Art piece.  This circle features the word "welcome" precisely cut out beneath a duck taking off mid-flight. The natural animal theme makes it a warm, welcoming gesture for any home. The Duck Welcome Circle Metal Art decor is the USA and flaunts the intricate artistry of metal artworks. If you love nature-themed displays, this would make an excellent choice as a greeting in your entrance hallway or even on the balcony. The tough, quality steel makes it suitable for indoors or outdoors, and the hammered black color provides a flexible decorating experience to match your home's decor.

title: Bronco Rider Welcome Circle by Dugout Creek Designs
description: Show off your true cowboy nature with the Bronco Rider Welcome Circle by Dugout Creek Designs Metal Art Decor - a design featuring a bucking bronco with a rider on the back. This is beautifully presented in a circle frame and the word "welcome" beneath, cut out intricately by hand in the USA. The Bronco Rider Welcome Circle Metal Art Decor is made of high-quality steel and comes in a modern hammered black tone or a rust-brown color to suit different decor styles. Place it on the front door entrance or in the entrance hallway of your home, farmhouse, cabin, hunting/fishing lodge, or anywhere else you'd like to spread the cowboy love. Better yet, if you can't think of a use for this welcome circle, you could also gift it to someone who loves embracing the cowboy, bronco-riding lifestyle.

title: Koko Baby Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art
description: Looking for a fun and unique way to spruce up your home décor? Check out Koko Baby Metal Decor by Meyerdirk Art.  It's perfect for adding a splash of color and personality to any room! Available in five vibrant colors (aged black, aged blue, aged orange, aged red, or aged teal), this southwest-inspired metal decor piece is sure to stand out. Each one is handmade in the USA from steel, so you can be assured of its quality and durability. And what’s more, Kokopelli is known as both a deity and fertility figure among the Ancient Pueblo People – making this an extra meaningful decoration for your home.

title: Reverse Lashes by Meyerdirk Art
description: A striking wall addition to any home, the Reverse Lashes by Meyerdirk Art will immediately capture the attention of your guests invited over, especially when placed in a common room like the living room or entrance hallway. Made with a high-quality steel construction at the hands of our expert metal artisans in the USA, this magnificent work of art details "reverse lashes" on a vivid color background of your choice. This selection of colors includes bright candy tones and a distressed copper color for a more "rustic" vibe. You can choose one that looks best for your home or office space. If you love statement pieces of art, these will no doubt be perfect for your decorating needs.  If you would like to see more pieces like Reverse Lashes, check out the Scar by Meyerdirk Art!

It is an outstanding individual piece available in bright metallic shades and high gloss finish. This sculpture can be hung from either end in any desired direction. It goes with all kinds of decorating styles and is available in a number of colors to spice up your space.

description: Hunters, nature-lovers, and those who love deer will definitely appeal to this Standing Deer Welcome Circle by Dugout Creek Designs. Featuring a standing deer framed by a circle border with the word "WELCOME" beneath, this metal art isn't just for decorating, but also as a special way to greet guests. The Standing Deer Welcome Circle Metal Art Decor is made from quality steel. It's handmade, so no two pieces will ever be exactly alike, giving it a unique, personalized touch. It looks perfect when set on its own at the entrance hallway or on a veranda, but it can be easily complimented with our other nature-themed pieces. This metal art design comes in a hammered black or rust patina finish, suitable for modern and rustic homes, respectively.
